PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FClassified documents seen by ITV News
OL,8,Fappear to show the gravest dangers
OL,9,Fposed by nature loss were not
OL,10,Fdisclosed to the public by the
OL,11,Fgovernment. ITV News Science
OL,12,FCorrespondent Martin Stew explains
OL,14,FWords by Senior Science Producer
OL,15,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,17,FITV News has seen a classified
OL,18,Fgovernment intelligence report which
OL,19,Fappears to show some of the most
OL,20,Fworrying potential impacts of nature
OL,21,Floss weren't disclosed to the public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FIn January, the government published a
OL,8,Freport on the security and economic
OL,9,Fthreats resulting from nature decline.
OL,11,FThe long-awaited government-
OL,12,Fcommissioned report had initially been
OL,13,Fscheduled for an autumn release.
OL,14,FAlthough the government received the
OL,15,Freport, it chose not to publish it and
OL,16,Fcancelled the launch. After pressure
OL,17,Ffrom campaign groups, including a
OL,18,Ffreedom of information request (FOI),
OL,19,Fit was released in January.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FHowever, a summary version was
OL,8,Fpublished, leaving out some of the key
OL,9,Fpoints experts had found.
OL,11,FITV News has seen extracts of the full
OL,12,Freport and can now reveal some of the
OL,13,Fwarnings the government chose not to
OL,14,Fpublish.
OL,16,FThe report, which was released
OL,17,Fpublicly, warns that drought, flooding
OL,18,Fand environmental decline could damage
OL,19,Fthe economy, but it does not offer any
OL,20,Fspecific figures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FThe full report shows that
OL,8,Fintelligence chiefs project that
OL,9,Fnature loss could lead to annual "GDP
OL,10,Fbeing 12% lower than it would have
OL,11,Fbeen otherwise by 2030."
OL,13,FTo contextualise, we spend around 11%
OL,14,Fof our GDP annually on the NHS.
OL,16,F"If we don't deal with nature loss,
OL,17,Fthe consequences of that could be as
OL,18,Fstark (as a 12% loss) - it's more than
OL,19,Fdouble what we saw in the financial
OL,20,Fcrisis," says Angela Francis, Director
OL,21,Fof Policy Solutions at WWF.
OL,26,@sD@XO]xD@AOUzD@GpmzD@Upn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,F"The government, rather than
OL,8,Fexplaining to people what it needs to
OL,9,Fdo to tackle those problems, is just
OL,10,Ftrying to hide from the problem
OL,11,Fbecause it knows that food prices and
OL,12,Fcost of living is such a concern."
OL,14,FFood security
OL,16,FThe UK currently grows around 60% of
OL,17,Fthe food we eat. The shorter report
OL,18,Fhighlights food security as a key
OL,19,Frisk, but the full report goes further.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FIt notes that the "UK (is)
OL,8,Fincreasingly exposed to state threats,
OL,9,Fparticularly if our food system
OL,10,Fbecomes a more vulnerable or desirable
OL,11,Ftarget." It also highlights the "risk
OL,12,Fof NATO being drawn into escalating
OL,13,Fconflicts over arable land" such as
OL,14,Fthe "breadbaskets" of Ukraine and
OL,15,FRussia.
OL,17,FLt Gen Richard Nugee is a retired
OL,18,FSenior British Army Officer and also a
OL,19,Fstrategic advisor for climate,
OL,20,Fsecurity and defence. He says the
OL,21,Freport is a "seminal" moment.
OL,26,@oD@WpmoD@ZpnsD@HO]sD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"It is very significant indeed," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"The government has admitted for the
OL,16,Ffirst time that climate and
OL,17,Fbiodiversity loss are parts of our
OL,18,Fnational security. They don't do that
OL,19,Flightly, and what that shows is that
OL,20,Factually, we should be concerned for
OL,21,Four security as a homeland.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,F"We must build our homeland resilience
OL,8,Fbecause otherwise we are putting our
OL,9,Fcitizens at risk."
OL,11,FNature and water security
OL,13,FThe published report also discusses
OL,14,Fthe collapse of global ecosystems,
OL,15,Fincluding rainforests and coral reefs.
OL,16,FBut some of the most concerning
OL,17,Fdetails are missing.
OL,26,@qD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
