PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FFor example, while it mentions the
OL,8,Frisk of diseases emerging as frozen
OL,9,Fground thaws in northern forests, the
OL,10,Fdocuments seen by ITV News
OL,11,Fspecifically reference "Anthrax" and
OL,12,Fthe potential for "mass mortality"
OL,13,Fevents in worst-case scenarios.
OL,26,@sD@XOUsD@`O]tD@SOUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
