OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FSimilarly, while the short report
OL,8,Fnotes the risk of water shortages in
OL,9,Fthe Himalayas, it omits the warnings
OL,10,FITV News has seen in the longer
OL,11,Fversion - that shrinking glaciers
OL,12,Fcould "almost certainly escalate
OL,13,Ftension" between China, India and
OL,14,FPakistan - increasing the "threat of
OL,15,Fnuclear exchanges".
OL,17,FAnother key impact of climate-induced
OL,18,Fnature degradation is the increase in
OL,19,Fmigration as people are forced to move
OL,20,Ffrom areas with increasingly scarce
OL,21,Fresources.
OL,26,@tD@GOUuD@HO]vD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
