SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FThe full report specifically warns of
OL,8,Fthe impact this will have in the UK,
OL,9,Fwith a potential rise in "polarised
OL,10,Fand populist politics", as well as
OL,11,Fpressure on national infrastructure.
OL,26,@qD@ZOU
