CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FITV News can exclusively reveal that
OL,8,F25 nature organisations, including the
OL,9,FRoyal Society for the Protection of
OL,10,FBirds (RSPB), World Wildlife Fund
OL,11,F(WWF) and the Wildlife Trusts, have
OL,12,Fwritten a letter to the government
OL,13,Fresponding to the original short
OL,14,Freport, demanding the government take
OL,15,Fit more seriously and take leadership
OL,16,Fon an international scale:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,F"It has huge impacts on our economy,
OL,8,Fon our future prosperity, on our
OL,9,Fhealth ` it has a lot that is riding
OL,10,Fon it. Our level of concern is
OL,11,Fparallel to that. We're saying, this
OL,12,Fis a really concerning report and we
OL,13,Fneed to act in a way that addresses
OL,14,Fthat," says Beccy Speight, the CEO of
OL,15,Fthe RSPB.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FQuestions remain over why the full
OL,8,Freport was not released, with some
OL,9,Finside sources suggesting it is
OL,10,Fbecause the government's own nature
OL,11,Fpolicies currently do not reflect the
OL,12,Fseverity of the report's conclusions.
OL,14,F"It needs to release the full report,
OL,15,Fand it needs to explain to the public
OL,16,Fhow it is going to start dealing with
OL,17,Fthose risks, rather than giving us a
OL,18,Fsanitised, simplified version and
OL,19,Fpretending it can brush it under the
OL,20,Fcarpet," says Angela Francis.
OL,26,@|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,F"If the public doesn't understand the
OL,8,Fgravity of the situation and what it
OL,9,Fcould do to this country, then they
OL,10,Fwill never apply pressure to the
OL,11,Fgovernment to actually do something
OL,12,Fsolid about it," says Lt Gen Richard
OL,13,FNugee.
OL,15,FITV News put all these claims to the
OL,16,FDepartment for Environment, Food and
OL,17,FRural Affairs (DEFRA), the government
OL,18,Fdepartment that published the report.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
