PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772244190
OL,3,CNature loss could cost twice as much
OL,4,Cas financial crash, leaked report
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FDEFRA declined an interview but said:
OL,8,F"Understanding the security risks
OL,9,Farising from biodiversity loss is
OL,10,Fcritical to strengthening the UK's
OL,11,Flong-term resilience, and this
OL,12,Fassessment will inform our actions to
OL,13,Fprepare the UK for the future.
OL,15,F"We are already investing a record
OL,16,F#11.8 billion in sustainable farming
OL,17,Fand #10.5 billion in flood defences at
OL,18,Fhome, as well as #3 billion to protect
OL,19,Fvital habitats around the world: all
OL,20,Fpart of our commitment to understand
OL,21,Fand prevent nature loss."
OL,26,@pD@AOU}D@YO]
